title: The UK During the 70 Year Reign of Elizabeth II
itunes:author: Professor Tim Besley, Dr Tania Burchardt, Professor Michael Cox, Sir Anthony Seldon
description: Contributor(s): Professor Tim Besley, Dr Tania Burchardt, Professor Michael Cox, Sir Anthony Seldon | This event explores how the UK has changed during the 70 years of the Queen’s reign and will consider how the UK’s: economy, government and politics, social policy and foreign relations have evolved between 1952 and 2022.
